---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About PlateDrop - Your Home Gym Deal Finder"
  description="Learn about PlateDrop's mission to help fitness enthusiasts find the best deals on quality home gym equipment. Daily curated deals, expert reviews, and honest recommendations."
>
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Building Your Dream Home Gym, One Deal at a Time</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          We're on a mission to make quality fitness equipment accessible to everyone through smart deal hunting and honest recommendations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            Home gym equipment shouldn't break the bank. We track prices across major retailers daily, 
            finding genuine deals on quality equipment so you can build your dream gym without overspending.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"></path>
              <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Quality First</h2>
          <p>
            Not all deals are created equal. We focus on reputable brands and retailers, ensuring every 
            deal we feature represents genuine value and quality equipment that will last.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Daily Updates</h2>
          <p>
            Prices change constantly. Our automated system checks deals every day, ensuring you never 
            miss out on limited-time offers or price drops on equipment you've been eyeing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>How PlateDrop Started</h2>
        <p>
          Like many fitness enthusiasts, we started building a home gym during the pandemic. What should 
          have been exciting quickly became frustrating‚Äîprices were inflated, stock was limited, and 
          finding genuine deals felt impossible.
        </p>
        <p>
          We spent hours comparing prices across different retailers, tracking price histories, and 
          waiting for the right moment to buy. That's when we realized: there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p>
          PlateDrop was born from that frustration. We built a system that does the heavy lifting‚Äîtracking 
          prices, validating deals, and curating the best offers daily. Now, instead of spending hours 
          hunting for deals, you can spend that time actually working out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What We Stand For</h2>
      
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üéØ Transparency</h3>
          <p>
            We're upfront about affiliate relationships and never let commissions influence our 
            recommendations. If it's not a good deal, we won't feature it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üìä Data-Driven</h3>
          <p>
            Every deal is validated against historical pricing data. We show you real savings, 
            not inflated "discounts" from artificial list prices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>ü§ù Community-Focused</h3>
          <p>
            We're building this for the home gym community. Your feedback shapes our features, 
            and your success stories inspire us to keep improving.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>üîí Privacy-Respecting</h3>
          <p>
            No tracking pixels, no data selling, no creepy retargeting. Just honest deal curation 
            and helpful content.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="retailers-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Retailers We Track</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        We monitor prices across the most trusted names in fitness equipment
      </p>
      
      <div class="retailers-grid">
        <div class="retailer-badge">Rogue Fitness</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">REP Fitness</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">Amazon</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">Titan Fitness</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">PowerBlock</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">Bowflex</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">CAP Barbell</div>
        <div class="retailer-badge">Yes4All</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Start Saving Today</h2>
        <p>
          Check out today's deals and see how much you can save on your home gym equipment.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">View Today's Deals</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding-block: var(--space-20) var(--space-16);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.05'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.1;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .hero-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  
  .mission-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }
  
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .content-block {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .content-block p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .story-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .story-content {
    max-width: 70ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  
  .story-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .story-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .values-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .section-description {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .value-card {
    padding: var(--space-8);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .value-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .retailers-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .retailers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  
  .retailer-badge {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .retailer-badge:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
  }
  
  .cta-card {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-12);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .cta-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    opacity: 0.95;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .btn-lg {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-8);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero {
      padding-block: var(--space-16) var(--space-12);
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    }
    
    .content-grid {
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
    
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .retailers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>